'''美利堅合眾國'''（{{lang-en|The United States of America}}、{{lang|en|U.S.A.}}、 {{lang|en|United States}}、{{lang|en|U.S.}}），简称'''美国'''（{{lang|en|America}}），是[[北美洲|北美洲]]的一个[[聯邦制|聯邦制]][[共和制|共和國]]，亦是當今世上唯一的[[超級強國|超級強國]]<ref name=":0" />，由下轄的50個[[美國州份|州]]加上[[联邦地区|联邦政府直辖]]的[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]、五個离岸[[美國領土#非合併建制領土|自治領土]]及[[美國本土外小島嶼|若干外島]]組成{{NoteTag|1=五個自治領土指[[美屬薩摩亞|美屬薩摩亞]]、[[關島|關島]]、[[北馬里亞納群島|北馬里亞納群島]]、[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]和[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]。另有11個無常住人口的島：[[貝克島|貝克島]]、[[豪蘭島|豪蘭島]]、[[賈維斯島|賈維斯島]]、[[約翰斯頓環礁|約翰斯頓環礁]]、[[金曼礁|金曼礁]]、[[中途島|中途島]]和[[帕邁拉環礁|帕邁拉環礁]]。美國關於[[巴霍努埃沃淺灘|巴霍努埃沃淺灘]]、[[納弗沙島|納弗沙島]]、[[塞拉尼拉淺灘|塞拉尼拉淺灘]]和[[威克島|威克島]]的領土主權存在爭議<ref>U.S. State Department, [http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/179780.htm Common Core Document to U.N. Committee on Human Rights] {{Wayback|url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/179780.htm |date=20170122211018 }}, 2011-12-30, Item 22, 27, 80.— and U.S. General Accounting Office Report, [http://www.gao.gov/archive/1998/og98005.pdf U.S. Insular Areas: application of the U.S. Constitution] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gao.gov/archive/1998/og98005.pdf |date=20131103093032 }}, November 1997, p. 1, 6, 39n. Both viewed 2016-04-06.</ref>}}。美国的官方领土面积為{{convert|9833520|km2}}<ref name="auto" />，为北美第二（次于[[加拿大|加拿大]]），并位居[[世界各国和地区面积列表|世界第三或第四]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=The World Factbook |url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2147rank.html |publisher=Central Intelligence Agency |access-date=2019-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209041128/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2147rank.html |archive-date=2014-02-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2020年初，美国[[美国人口|总人口]]約為3.3億人<ref name="clock">{{cite web|title=Population Clock|url=https://www.census.gov/popclock/|publisher=United States Census Bureau|access-date=2019-03-01|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025617/http://www.census.gov/popclock/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，僅次於[[中國|中國]]及[[印度|印度]]，是[[國家人口列表|世界第三人口大国]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=U.S. Census Bureau Current Population|url=https://www.census.gov/popclock/print.php?component=counter|access-date=2019-03-01|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302090517/https://www.census.gov/popclock/print.php?component=counter|archive-date=2019-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Improved Race and Ethnicity Measures Reveal U.S. Population Is Much More Multiracial|url=https://www.census.gov/library/stories/2021/08/improved-race-ethnicity-measures-reveal-united-states-population-much-more-multiracial.html|access-date=2021-09-28|last=Bureau|first=US Census|work=The United States Census Bureau|language=EN-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021091045/https://www.census.gov/library/stories/2021/08/improved-race-ethnicity-measures-reveal-united-states-population-much-more-multiracial.html|archive-date=2021-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>、人口最多的[[发达国家|发达国家]]。美国與其它[[西方世界|西方國家]]，包括[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[澳大利亚|澳洲]]、[[新西兰|紐西蘭]]等，同樣有着來自世界各地的大量[[移民|移民]]，是世界上[[美国种族及民族|民族]]和[[多元文化主义|文化]]最多元的國家之一<ref name="DD">Adams, J.Q.; Strother-Adams, Pearlie (2001). ''Dealing with Diversity''. Chicago: Kendall/Hunt. ISBN 0-7872-8145-X.</ref>，有“民族[[大熔炉|大熔炉]]”之称。美國[[美国地理|国土的地形与气候]]複雜多样，[[生物多样性|生物多样性]]齐全，是多种野生动植物的主要家园<ref>{{Cite web |title=Wildlife Library |url=http://www.nwf.org/wildlife.aspx |accessdate=2014-12-23 |publisher=National Wildlife Federation |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108112122/http://www.nwf.org/wildlife.aspx |archive-date=2016-11-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[欧洲人|欧洲人]]从16世纪开始[[美洲殖民|殖民北美]]，而现今的合众国起始于[[美国东岸|东海岸]]的[[十三殖民地|13个英属美洲殖民地]]<ref name="auto1">{{Cite book |title=United States History: Independence to 1914 |last=（美）William Deverell 等 编著 |date=1999 |publisher=Holt Rinehart Winston |isbn=0-03-041228-5 |language=en-US}}</ref>。在欧洲[[七年战争|七年战争]]后，[[大不列顛王國|大不列顛王國]]与其海外殖民地之间的矛盾愈发剧烈，最终导致在1775年爆发[[美国革命|美国革命]]。1776年7月4日，正与[[大不列颠及爱尔兰联合王国|大不列颠]]进行[[美国独立战争|独立战争]]的各[[殖民地|殖民地]]派出代表，协同一致發表《[[美國獨立宣言|独立宣言]]》。戰爭終止於1783年，[[大不列顛王國|大不列顛王國]]承认這13個北美殖民地脫離管辖而独立，与其簽訂《[[巴黎條約_(1783年)|巴黎條約]]》<ref name="auto1" />。这场战争也是第一场成功脱离欧洲[[殖民帝国|殖民帝国]]的独立战争<ref>Greene, Jack P.; Pole, J.R., eds. (2008). ''A Companion to the American Revolution''. pp. 352–361.<br />{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wQHlrIz4gpYC&pg=PA61 |title=A Nation Among Nations: America's Place in World History |last=Bender |first=Thomas |publisher=Hill & Wang |year=2006 |isbn=978-0-8090-7235-4 |location=New York |page=61 |access-date=2016-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160912194047/https://books.google.com/books?id=wQHlrIz4gpYC&pg=PA61 |archive-date=2016-09-12 |dead-url=no }}<br />{{Cite web |title=Overview of the Early National Period |url=http://www.digitalhistory.uh.edu/era.cfm?eraid=4&smtid=1 |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |year=2014 |publisher=University of Houston |website=Digital History |access-date=2015-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150212073754/http://www.digitalhistory.uh.edu/era.cfm?eraid=4&smtid=1 |archive-date=2015-02-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1781年，《[[邦联条例|邦联条例]]》在邦聯13個構成州获得通过，共同组成了[[邦聯議會_(美國)|邦聯議會]]，各實體組成了國家聯盟，1787年《[[美利堅合眾國憲法|美利堅合眾國憲法]]》完稿，合併一國後將邦聯體制升級為[[聯邦|聯邦]]，「美利堅合眾國」联邦政府随之成立。1791年，合称为[[美國權利法案|权利法案]]的十条[[美国宪法修正案|宪法修正案]]獲得批准，担保了基本民权<ref>{{Cite web |title=U.S. Bill of Rights |url=https://www.constitutionfacts.com/us-constitution-amendments/bill-of-rights/ |publisher=Oak Hill Publishing Company. |access-date=2019-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302024729/https://www.constitutionfacts.com/us-constitution-amendments/bill-of-rights/ |archive-date=2019-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自[[19世紀|19世紀]]起美國從獨立时的英裔殖民地國家開始轉向[[美国西进运动|西进]]和[[美国领土扩张|對外擴張]]，[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦政府]]先后通过[[路易斯安那购地|1803年]]和[[亚当斯－奥尼斯条约|1819年]]两次购地、[[俄勒冈条约|与英属殖民地谈判]]、[[美墨战争|击败墨西哥]]和[[北美印第安戰爭|屠杀并强行迁移原住民]]等方法获得了[[北纬49度线|北纬49度线]]以南、[[格兰德河|格兰德河]]中游以北的几乎所有土地，并从[[沙俄|沙俄]]手中[[阿拉斯加易手|购得阿拉斯加]]。这期間陸續有許多新建立的殖民地政体申請加入美国聯邦，随着逐渐不断地[[美国州份依加入联邦顺序排列列表|承认扩张领地为新州份]]，至1848年时[[美國領土變遷|美国疆域]]已横跨整个北美大陆<ref name="MD2007">{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/?id=ka6LxulZaEwC&vq=annexation&dq=territorial+expansion+United+States+%22manifest+destiny%22 |title=Manifest Destiny and the Expansion of America |last=Carlisle |first=Rodney P. |last2=Golson |first2=J. Geoffrey |publisher=ABC-CLIO |year=2007 |isbn=978-1-85109-833-0 |series=Turning Points in History Series |page=238}}</ref>。在19世纪下半叶，[[美国南部|美国南部]]七个[[蓄奴州|蓄奴州]]宣布退出聯邦獨立并成立[[美利坚邦联国|美利坚邦联国]]，因而爆发[[南北戰争|內戰]]，但後來被[[林肯|林肯]]领导的[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]以武力重新併吞，使曾在南方诸州合法的[[美国奴隶制度|奴隶制度]]得以被终结<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Civil War and emancipation 1861–1865 |url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/aia/part4/4p2967.html |year=1999 |work=Africans in America |publisher=WGBH Educational Foundation |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19991012054217/http://pbs.org/wgbh/aia/part4/4p2967.html |archivedate=1999-10-12 |location=Boston, Massachusetts |access-date=2016-09-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com/?id=T_0TrXXiDbUC&dq=slavery+%22American+Civil+War%22 |title=The American Civil War and Reconstruction: People, Politics, and Power |last=Britannica Educational Publishing |publisher=Rosen Publishing Group |year=2009 |isbn=978-1-61530-045-7 |editor-first=Jeffrey H. |series=America at War |page=264 |editor1-last=Wallenfeldt}}</ref>。在19世纪末，美国已将其领土[[主权|主权]]延伸到[[太平洋|太平洋]]的[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]，并在[[第二次工业革命|第二次工业革命]]的推动下开始了[[镀金时代|镀金时代]]和[[进步时代|进步时代]]的蓬勃发展期<ref>{{Cite web |title=Work in the Late 19th Century |url=http://www.loc.gov/teachers/classroommaterials/presentationsandactivities/presentations/timeline/riseind/work/ |accessdate=2015-01-16 |website=Library of Congress |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106142226/http://www.loc.gov/teachers/classroommaterials/presentationsandactivities/presentations/timeline/riseind/work/ |archive-date=2015-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后[[美西战争|美西战争]]的胜利，美国對外干涉的範圍超過現在的美國本土，使美国势力进入[[加勒比海地区|加勒比海地区]]及[[西太平洋|西太平洋]]。

进入[[20世纪|20世纪]]后，美国在[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]后期参战并奠定了其作为一个全球性军事力量的基础。尽管在[[咆哮的二十年代|咆哮的二十年代]]结束后，美国在1930年代迎来了[[大蕭條|經濟大蕭條]]，但是在[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]獲得勝利之后美国迅速崛起成为[[超级大国|超级大国]]。作为[[联合国安全理事会|联合国安全理事会]]五个[[联合国安全理事会常任理事国|常任理事国]]之一，美國不僅是[[核武器|核武]]擁有國，亦是世界上第一个研发出[[核武器|核武器]]，並唯一[[廣島與長崎原子彈爆炸|曾将其投入实战]]的国家<ref name="NWA">{{Cite web |title=Gallery of U.S. Nuclear Tests |url=http://nuclearweaponarchive.org/Usa/Tests/index.html |date=2001-08-06 |website=The Nuclear Weapon Archive |access-date=2019-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831222339/http://nuclearweaponarchive.org/Usa/Tests/index.html |archive-date=2009-08-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。二战后美国与[[苏联|苏联]]因[[意识形态|意识形态]]和[[地缘政治|地缘政治]]竞争进行了數十年的[[冷戰|冷戰]]，在对峙顶峰时期的[[太空竞赛|太空竞赛]]亦促使了[[阿波罗11号|人类第一次登月计划]]的成功。在20世紀90年代初[[苏联解体|苏联解体]]后，被廣泛視為當今世上唯一的[[超級強國|超級強國]]<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title=Putin: Russia respects U.S. as world's "only superpower"|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/vladimir-putin-russia-respects-us-world-superpower/|accessdate=2021-12-08|website=CBS news|publisher=CBS news|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227025154/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/vladimir-putin-russia-respects-us-world-superpower/|archive-date=2022-02-27|dead-url=no|author1=CBS news}}</ref>。

美国自19世紀末开始就已成为世界第一大经济体<ref name="Digital History">{{cite web|author1=Digital History |author2=Steven Mintz |url=http://www.digitalhistory.uh.edu/database/article_display.cfm?HHID=188 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040302193732/http://www.digitalhistory.uh.edu/database/article_display.cfm?HHID=188 |archive-date=2004-03-02 |title=Digital History |publisher=Digitalhistory.uh.edu |access-date=2012-04-21 }}</ref>，長期以來都是全球的經濟<ref>{{cite web |author1=World Population Review |title=GDP Ranked by Country 2021 |url=https://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/countries-by-gdp |website=World Population Review |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2022-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220228180953/https://worldpopulationreview.com/countries/countries-by-gdp |dead-url=no }}</ref>、軍事<ref>{{cite web |author1=Global Firepower |title=2021 Military Strength Ranking |url=https://www.globalfirepower.com/countries-listing.php |website=Global Firepower |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2021-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321035351/https://www.globalfirepower.com/countries-listing.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>、教育<ref>{{cite web |author1=QS Top Universities |title=The World's Top 100 Universities |url=https://www.topuniversities.com/student-info/choosing-university/worlds-top-100-universities |website=QS Top Universities |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2022-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227025414/https://www.topuniversities.com/student-info/choosing-university/worlds-top-100-universities |dead-url=no }}</ref>、科研<ref>{{cite web |author1=SJR |title=Scimago Journal & Country Rank |url=https://www.scimagojr.com/countryrank.php |website=SJR |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806194649/http://www.scimagojr.com/countryrank.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>、航天<ref>{{cite web |author1=World Population Review |title=Countries With Space Programs 2021 |url=https://worldpopulationreview.com/country-rankings/countries-with-space-programs |website=World Population Review |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2022-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227031441/https://worldpopulationreview.com/country-rankings/countries-with-space-programs |dead-url=no }}</ref>及醫療技術<ref>{{cite web |author1=areppim AG, Switzerland |title=Global Ranking of Academic Subjects 2019 Medical Technology |url=https://stats.areppim.com/stats/stats_uni2019med_tec.htm |website=areppim AG, Switzerland |access-date=2021-12-08 |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210010710/https://stats.areppim.com/stats/stats_uni2019med_tec.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>的頭號強國。美国作为一个高度发达国家，是世界上最大的進口國及第二大的商品出口國<ref>{{Cite web |title=Leading import countries worldwide in 2017 (in billion U.S. dollars) |url=https://www.statista.com/statistics/268184/leading-import-countries-worldwide/ |publisher=Statiska |access-date=2019-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190302090510/https://www.statista.com/statistics/268184/leading-import-countries-worldwide/ |archive-date=2019-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Leading export countries worldwide in 2017 (in billion U.S. dollars) |url=https://www.statista.com/statistics/264623/leading-export-countries-worldwide/ |publisher=Statiska |access-date=2019-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190331112605/https://www.statista.com/statistics/264623/leading-export-countries-worldwide/ |archive-date=2019-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[國內生產总值|國內生產总值]]按國際匯率[[各國國內生產總值列表_(國際匯率)|排名世界第一]]、而依購買力平均則[[各國國內生產總值列表_(購買力平價)|位列第二]]。在国民平均薪資<ref>{{Cite web |title=Average annual wages, 2013 USD PPPs and 2013 constant prices |url=http://stats.oecd.org//Index.aspx?QueryId=64115 |accessdate=2016-04-30 |website=OECD |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505054502/http://stats.oecd.org//index.aspx?queryid=64115 |archive-date=2016-05-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[人類發展指數|人類發展指數]]、[[各國人均國内生產總值列表_(國際匯