=== 医疗保健 ===
{{Main|美國醫療系統}}
根据[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]1997年的医疗系统总体表现排名，美国在世卫组织会员国中名列第15位。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Overall Health system attainment in all Member States, WHO index, estimates for 1997 |url=http://www.who.int/whr/2000/en/annex09_en.pdf |accessdate=2006-1129 |publisher=World Health Organization |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070128232928/http://www.who.int/whr/2000/en/annex09_en.pdf |archive-date=2007-01-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>以占[[国民生产总值|国民总产值]]比例和人均花费指标衡量，美国在健康方面的花费（私人和公共花费共计）远超其他国家。<ref>''OECD Health Data 2000: A Comparative Analysis of 29 Countries'' (Paris: OECD, 2000); see also [http://dll.umaine.edu/ble/U.S.%20HCweb.pdf "The US Healthcare System: The Best in the World or Just the Most Expensive?] {{Wayback|url=http://dll.umaine.edu/ble/U.S.%20HCweb.pdf |date=20070421103048 }} 2001. The University of Main. Accessed 29 November 2006.</ref>然而，如此高的支出并未提供水准相应的公共健康保障。[[中央情报局|中央情报局]][[世界概况|世界概况]]的资料表明，美国与其他西方工业化国家相比，婴儿死亡率较高，国民平均壽命略低於[[瑞典|瑞典]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=CIA factbook, Germany health |url=https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/gm.html#People |accessdate=2006-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061101000629/https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/gm.html#People |archivedate=2006-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和[[法国|法国]]<ref name="CIA factbook, France health">{{Cite web |title=CIA factbook, France health |url=https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/fr.html#People |accessdate=2006-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061031225825/https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/fr.html#People |archivedate=2006-10-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="CIA factbook, US health">{{Cite web |title=CIA factbook, US health |url=https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/us.html#People |accessdate=2006-10-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20061101002837/https://www.cia.gov/cia/publications/factbook/geos/us.html#People |archivedate=2006-11-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>等国。美国医生的平均工资是世界最高的。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Cross-National Comparisons Of Health Systems Using OECD Data, 1999 - Reinhardt et al. 21(3):169 - Health Affairs |url=http://content.healthaffairs.org/cgi/content/abstract/21/3/169?maxtoshow=&HITS=10&hits=10&RESULTFORMAT=&fulltext=cross-national+comparison&andorexactfulltext=and&searchid=1&FIRSTINDEX=0&resourcetype=HWCIT |accessdate=2017-05-23 |author=Uwe E. Reinhardt, Peter S. Hussey and Gerard F. Anderson |publisher=Content.healthaffairs.org |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090830151110/http://content.healthaffairs.org/cgi/content/abstract/21/3/169?maxtoshow=&HITS=10&hits=10&RESULTFORMAT=&fulltext=cross-national+comparison&andorexactfulltext=and&searchid=1&FIRSTINDEX=0&resourcetype=HWCIT |archive-date=2009-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>但[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]仍是[[公共卫生|公共卫生]]难题，估计造成的年度医疗开支达数百亿美元。在統計上美國中低收入者肥胖比率偏高。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/3418603.stm "Obesity cost US $75bn, says study" by Jannat Jalil] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/3418603.stm |date=20070628164938 }}. 21 January 2004. ''BBC''. Retrieved on 5 October 2006.</ref>

与其他[[西方世界|西方]]国家不同，美国保健制度不是完全公费，而是公私共同支付，美國並無全民健保，美國總統[[比尔·克林顿|柯林頓]]任內其妻希拉里曾花費許多心力想建立全民健保，讓美國人人有醫療保險，然而卻被國會與利益團體否決掉。据2004年资料，个人健康花费中私营保险业支付占36%，个人占15%，联邦、州和地方政府占44%。<ref>[http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/hus/hus06.pdf Health, United States, 2006] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/hus/hus06.pdf |date=20070421223251 }}. U.S. Department of Health and Human Services, Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, National Center for Health Statistics.</ref>在2005年，4120万居民（美国总人口的14.2%）至少在该年度的某一段时间没有医疗保险；不过其中三分之一家庭收入超过5万美元，而这类人口又有一半人收入超过7.5万美元。<ref>[http://www.census.gov/hhes/www/hlthins/hlthin05.html Income, Poverty, and Health Insurance Coverage in the United States: 2005.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.census.gov/hhes/www/hlthins/hlthin05.html |date=20070324080942 }} U.S. Census Bureau.</ref>另外，够资格加入公费医疗保险的人有三分之一未加入。医疗保险在美国传统上属于雇员福利。同时，无论病人是否有能力支付费用，医院必须提供急诊服务，然而急診之後醫院可趕走付不出錢的病人。在美国，医药费是导致个人破产的最大因素。<ref>[http://content.healthaffairs.org/cgi/content/full/hlthaff.w5.63/DC1 "Illness And Injury As Contributors To Bankruptcy"] {{Wayback|url=http://content.healthaffairs.org/cgi/content/full/hlthaff.w5.63/DC1 |date=20060712102635 }}, by David U. Himmelstein, Elizabeth Warren, Deborah Thorne, and Steffie Woolhandler, published at Health Affairs journal in 2005, ''Accessed 05 October 2006''.</ref>美国在医疗研究投入了巨额资金，大多数为私人投资。据2000年统计，私营非盈利机构投入占7%，私营企业占57%，税金支持的[[国立卫生研究院_(美国)|国立卫生研究院]]占36%。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hsc.utoledo.edu/research/nih_research_benefits.pdf |title=The Benefits of Medical Research and the Role of the NIH |access-date=2007-01-12 |archive-date=2007-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070616093810/http://hsc.utoledo.edu/research/nih_research_benefits.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
